UID:71dd05db3d62c9f3cebd9e52fe753ecf@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:There is still time to apply!! Click the "Register" button to 
 apply to be a Vendor\, Young Entrepreneur\, or Sponsor! Get ready for an u
 nforgettable day at the 44th Annual Meet in the Street Festival on May 2\,
  2026\, from 10 am to 4 pm in downtown Wake Forest! This vibrant celebrati
 on is the largest event in town\, showcasing over 100 artisan booths\, fil
 led with unique handmade treasures\, a mouthwatering array of food trucks 
 in two courts\, and entertainment spread throughout the event! Families wi
 ll love the Children's Village\, bursting with fun activities for kids of 
 all ages\, and NEW this year\, Engine Alley- home to over 20 unique vehicl
 es! . With free admission\, there's no reason to miss out on this incredib
 le festival!
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/meet-in-the
 -street-2026
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
