BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:AI Series: AI Strategy & Ethics for Long-Term Growth
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T080000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260317T093000
UID:add1d838c7608fc4cdfbf0ee9f2436d5@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:As AI becomes more embedded in daily operations\, businesses m
 ust think beyond tools and focus on long-term strategy\, responsibility\, 
 and trust. This session explores how to align AI adoption wiht your organi
 zation's values\, goals\, and governance needs. Participants will examine 
 responsible AI practices\, data privacy considerations\, and transparency 
 standards that support sustainable growth while managing risk. You'll expl
 ore: Responsible AI use and ethical considerations Data privacy\, transpar
 ency\, and governance frameworks Aligning AI initiatives with long-term bu
 siness goals
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/ai-series-a
 i-strategy-ethics-for-long-term-growth
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:AI Series: Building an AI-Enhanced Website & Chatbot
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T120000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T133000
UID:dbe7bcdd0d1fbc4c6356dcb8a5d637e3@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Your website can do more than share information- it can active
 ly engage visitors\, capture leads\, and support customers around the cloc
 k. This practical session introduces no-code tools that make it easy to ad
 d AI-powered features to your website\, including chatbots designed for cu
 stomer service\, lead generation\, and basic support. Participants will ex
 plore how AI can enhance user experience without complex development or te
 chnical expertise.
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/ai-series-b
 uilding-an-ai-enhanced-website-chatbot
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:AI Series: AI-Powered Content Strategy
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260513T080000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260513T093000
UID:f516658c1b3ebb7b716d59a840b54c01@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Creating consistent\, high-quality content doesn't have to be 
 overwhelming. This session shows how AI tools can support content planning
 \, writing\, and mulitmedia creation- while keeping your message authentic
  and aligned with your brand. Participants will explore how AI can enhance
  SEO\, streamline long-form writing\, and support video and audio content 
 production. The focus is on practical workflows that save time and help ma
 intain a steady\, strategic content presence.
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/ai-series-a
 i-powered-content-strategy
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
