BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Business After Hours
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T160000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T180000
UID:1f77f0a4ad804f1824f4e4074f2ecf44@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exciting Business After Hours at Capitol Range 
 & Firearms! Connect with fellow professionals from across the community wh
 ile experiencing one of the Triangle’s most unique venues. This premier 
 indoor shooting facility features 20 climate-controlled shooting lanes\, a
  cutting-edge digital live-fire range\, firearm training classrooms\, a re
 tail shop\, and a VIP lounge designed for private and corporate events. Du
 ring the evening\, guests will mingle in the lounge and enjoy networking\,
  light refreshments\, and the opportunity to explore the facility and lear
 n more about the advanced technology and experiences offered. Whether you
 ’re new to shooting sports or simply looking for a fun and different net
 working atmosphere\, this event promises a memorable evening of connection
  and discovery. Bring plenty of business cards and join us for a high-ener
 gy networking event in a truly one-of-a-kind setting!
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/business-af
 ter-hours-03-19-2026
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
